issue.title: [CF 589] zhCN localization issue
issue.body:
zhCN localization for static format "ICONMENU_MULTISTATECD_DESC" has a second "%s" which caused an error on version 6.0.2 Release.

StaticFormats.lua line 26:
bad argument #2 to 'format' (string expected, got no value)


> Posted by CurseForge user Tellaurea | Imported from CurseForge issue #589 | Raw

comments.body:
Issue has already been resolved in the latest alpha.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
